OL,3,CHair salon owner says rising costs
OL,4,Cwill 'wipe out' apprenticeship
OL,5,Copportunities
OL,7,FThe owner of a hair salon in Kent has
OL,8,Fsaid the measures set out in the
OL,9,FAutumn Budget by Rachel Reeves will
OL,10,F"wipe out" apprenticeship
OL,11,Fopportunities in the profession.
OL,13,FToby Dicker runs The Chapel in
OL,14,FSevenoaks, which has 70 employees. He
OL,15,Falso formed the Salon Employers
OL,16,FAssociation, made up of 2,500 members,
OL,17,Fwhich grouped together with other
OL,18,Forganisations to create the British
OL,19,FHair Consortium.
