OL,3,CHair salon owner says rising costs
OL,4,Cwill 'wipe out' apprenticeship
OL,5,Copportunities
OL,7,FToby said rising costs and an unfair
OL,8,Ftax system are driving the industry to
OL,9,Fbreaking point. He is warning that
OL,10,Fapprenticeships will be "wiped out"
OL,11,Fbecause they are now too expensive for
OL,12,Fbusinesses, in part due to the
OL,13,Fincreasing minimum wage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
