OL,3,CHair salon owner says rising costs
OL,4,Cwill 'wipe out' apprenticeship
OL,5,Copportunities
OL,7,FHe said: "We had a Confederation of
OL,8,FBritish Industry (CBI) report written
OL,9,Fin February 2025. We got together and
OL,10,Fwe found out the facts of what's going
OL,11,Fon. Apprenticeships had already
OL,12,Fdropped by 75% in our sector from
OL,13,F16,000 down to around 4,000. We
OL,14,Fpredict a complete wiping out of that
OL,15,Fby 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
