OL,3,CHair salon owner says rising costs
OL,4,Cwill 'wipe out' apprenticeship
OL,5,Copportunities
OL,7,F"Apprenticeship wage has more than
OL,8,Fdoubled since 2020, 110% more when you
OL,9,Finclude the NICs and taxes in a cost
OL,10,Fto a business. What happens? They get
OL,11,Fwiped out, so young people will have
OL,12,Fno opportunities.
OL,14,F"A friend of mine had 500 applications
OL,15,Ffor 12 places the other day. Young
OL,16,Fpeople have got no opportunities of
OL,17,Fcoming to this sector. It's pretty
OL,18,Fmuch finished."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
