OL,7,FWhat changes are on the horizon for
OL,8,Fthe national minimum wage and the
OL,9,Fnational living wage?
OL,11,FThe national minimum wage and the
OL,12,Fnational living wage will rise from
OL,13,FApril, boosting the pay of around 2.7
OL,14,Fmillion people.
