OL,3,CHair salon owner says rising costs
OL,4,Cwill 'wipe out' apprenticeship
OL,5,Copportunities
OL,7,FThis will mean an annual earnings
OL,8,Fincrease of #1,500 for a full-time
OL,9,Fworker.
OL,11,FThe national living wage for 16 to 17-
OL,12,Fyear-olds and those on apprenticeships
OL,13,Fwill increase by 6% to #8 an hour.
OL,15,FToby said he's all for fair wages but
OL,16,Fnot if there aren't measures which
OL,17,Fease the financial pressure on
OL,18,Fbusinesses, like a reduction in VAT.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
