OL,3,CHair salon owner says rising costs
OL,4,Cwill 'wipe out' apprenticeship
OL,5,Copportunities
OL,7,FHe explains that he was hoping the
OL,8,Fgovernment would introduce a level
OL,9,Fplaying field, by taxing self-employed
OL,10,Ftraders who won't pay as much.
OL,12,F"I really, really hoped they'd be
OL,13,Fbrave enough to change tax policy, to
OL,14,Fmake all businesses pay the same
OL,15,Famount of VAT and level the tax
OL,16,Fplaying field. But what they've
OL,17,Factually done is widened it once
OL,18,Fagain", Toby said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
