OL,3,CHair salon owner says rising costs
OL,4,Cwill 'wipe out' apprenticeship
OL,5,Copportunities
OL,7,F"Ask Rachel Reeves, ask a Labour
OL,8,Fpolitician, do they want to see
OL,9,Femployment wiped out in the entire
OL,10,Fsector? That's what I'd ask them right
OL,11,Fnow because that's what's gonna happen.
OL,13,F"There'll be people like me who can
OL,14,Fsurvive. We have to charge 50% more
OL,15,Fjust to stand still, and we're going
OL,16,Fto do that because we want to do the
OL,17,Fright thing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
